 when the task can be split into multiple independent searches which will ultimately be synthesized.\n    This tool is never executed directly, but is intercepted by the router to tringger the fan-out pattern via Send.', 'parameters': {'properties': {'queries': {'description': 'Run multiple simultaneous standalone search queries for research to be done in parallel. Each item should be a full natural-language search statement or question, independent of the others. ', 'items': {'type': 'string'}, 'type': 'array'}}, 'required': ['queries'], 'type': 'object'}}}]}}
